      "author_association" : "NONE",
      "body" : "@MarcoFalke: I believe you have closed this issue without due consideration. When the user has sent a payment using `subtractfeefromamount`, they have already given explicit permission to deliver less than the requested amount to the requested recipient. Thus, it would **not** be unsafe for `bumpfee` to reduce the amount even further in this case. Besides, quite often when using `subtractfeefromamount`, the recipient is the same entity as the sender.",
